snippet: Threats of an attack on one of the crucial parts of the Internet have not had a measurable impact, said several people monitoring the Domain Name System.
abstract: Several people monitoring the Domain Name System say threats of an attack on one of the crucial parts of the Internet by members of the hacker collective Anonymous have not had a measurable impact.
lead_paragraph: Threats of an attack on one of the crucial parts of the Internet have not had a measurable impact, said several people monitoring the Domain Name System.

headline.seo: No Signs of Threatened Anonymous Attack on Internet
headline.main: After Threats, No Signs of Attack by Hackers
headline.print_headline: After Threats, No Signs Of Attack By Hackers
